</p>
<figcaption>Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - New Free Characters Update<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B0DHucYYD0k" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></figcaption></figure>


<p>
Last up is Tangle and Whisper, dual characters from the Sonic the Hedgehog spin-off comic series that debuted in 2019. Tangle is a lemur and Whisper is a wolf.
</p>
<p>
These three will join Persona 5's Joker and Like A Dragon's Ichiban, who were both recently added to the game as free additions.
</p>
<p>
Shortly after the game's release, the paid Minecraft DLC was released, featuring new characters and a new track. Capcom's <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/sonic-racing-crossworlds-adds-mega-man-next-year-with-post-launch-roadmap-now-revealed">Mega Man will also join next year</a>.
</p>

